title: Birmingham's Trinity Taylor tells us why she'll be a killer queen on 'RuPaul's Drag Race'
text: She'll compete on Season Nine of the Logo series, along with 12 other queens who are determined to dazzle the judges with their charisma, uniqueness, nerve and talent. Taylor, a Birmingham native who lives in Orlando, Fla., promises to be a standout on the show, if early video clips offer any indication.
